    About this hotel

    This modern budget hotel is 6 km from the football matches at Stade Ibn Batouta, 11 km from the Caves of Hercules and 14 km from the Forbes Museum of Tangier.

    The functional rooms come with free Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs. Some rooms feature bunk beds.

    Parking is complimentary. An all-you-can-eat breakfast buffet is served in a casual, bright dining room (fee).
